Installation
------------

# activate mercurial patch stack
$ cat >> ~/.hgrc
[extensions]
mq =

# clone patches repository including the dwm repository
$ hg qclone ssh://hg@bitbucket.org/jceb81/dwm-patches

# activate all patches, including the personal configuration
$ hg qpush -a

# build dwm
$ make

